Package: rtdown.molit
Type: Package
Title: Interactive MOLIT Real-Estate Transaction Downloader
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R:
    person("Derick S.", "Park", email = "soonmai@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive command-line downloader for the Korean Ministry of
    Land, Infrastructure and Transport (MOLIT) real-estate transaction
    APIs (RTMSDataSvc family). Supports four property types — apartments,
    multi-family ('연립다세대'), detached / multi-household ('단독·다가구'),
    and officetels — across both sale and rental endpoints, exposed via
    four entry points ('rtdown_apt()', 'rtdown_RH()', 'rtdown_SH()',
    'rtdown_O()') that share an identical five-step menu flow
    (자료 유형 → 시도 → 시군구 또는 시도 전체 → 시작 연월 → 종료 연월).
    Returns a tidy 'tibble' of every transaction in the requested range.
